                            <comment id="17495444" author="pkarwasz" created="Mon, 21 Feb 2022 10:23:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;To me it also seems like a bug in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/logging-log4j2/blob/e0a53b06c67769b87f5bf3c67681cbd2fa5b1cd6/log4j-1.2-api/src/main/java/org/apache/log4j/Category.java#L310&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;Category#forcedLog&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/logging-log4j2/blob/e0a53b06c67769b87f5bf3c67681cbd2fa5b1cd6/log4j-1.2-api/src/main/java/org/apache/log4j/Category.java#L561&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;Category#maybeLog&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: not all maps are String maps.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This should probably be refactored into a special &lt;tt&gt;MessageFactory&lt;/tt&gt; for Log4j 1.x bridge. I could write a PR tonight.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
